                "Below 52W high: %{customdata[0]:.1f}%<br>"
                "20D realized vol: %{customdata[1]:.1%}<br>"
                "Three-month return: %{customdata[2]:.1%}<br>"
                "20D avg volume: %{customdata[3]:,.0f}<br>"
                "Avg value traded: $%{customdata[4]:,.0f}<br>"
